{
  "stem": "24163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in Jerusalem, they have an Avenue of the Righteous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some of these people, who saved my family, where inducted in this Avenue of the Righteous, in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they were survivors, but not all of them were survivors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were all relatives.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were sisters of my dad, and their families, and the children, my-- my cousins, that were saved.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, late during the war, I might as well mention, since we talk about that period of time, when we were able to get out-- and we'll come back to that-- my grandmother, the one I spoke about earlier, she was fortunate enough to get out of Germany, to Holland, to live with her daughters.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, she was then, after Germany occupied Holland, she was caught in one of the many raids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to the best of my knowledge, she was, of course, killed in a-- in a camp, either near Riga or in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somewhere, there are records to show where my grandmother was killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the Nazis killed my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At the age of 84 is when they picked her up and-- and deported her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because there were riots in the streets of Gelsenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a very strong Communist and Social Democrat movement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a lot of mine workers who were members of the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Nazis opposed the Communists.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had street brawls and fights.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I witnessed some of those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I also witnessed when these-- the stormtroopers, as well as the Communists, went marching down the streets of our town with flags, and banners, and what have you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was in the early 1930s, so I was very much aware of the Nazi movement coming online.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
